@startuml
title Activity Diagram - Generate Test Cases for Feature

skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam activity {
    BackgroundColor LightSteelBlue
    BorderColor #0066CC
}

|User|
start
:Click "Generate with AI" button\n(Feature ID);

|System|
:Receive test case generation request;
:Get feature data from MongoDB\n(name, description, type,\nmatchedSections, reasoning);

if (Feature has matchedSections?) then (Yes)
    :Get context from matchedSections\n(3 chunks per section);
    note right: Using feature's matched sections
endif

:Get general context\n(1 query based on feature);

:Remove duplicate chunks;
:Combine all contexts;

:Build prompt\n(based on feature type);
note right: Prompt adapted to feature type\n(FUNCTIONAL, DATA, etc.)

:Invoke OpenAI LLM\n(GPT-4o-mini, JSON mode);
note right: LLM processing...

:Receive JSON test cases response;

:Parse JSON\n(Retry up to 3 times if needed);

:Validate test cases\n(Check required fields);

:Enhance test cases\n(Set defaults, Normalize priority,\nGenerate testCaseId);

:Save test cases to MongoDB;

:Store test case embeddings\nin Supabase;

:Return test cases array;

|User|
:See progress indicator;
:See success notification;
:Review generated test cases\nin test cases list;
:Edit or delete test cases as needed;
stop

@enduml
